name: Stash General Settings Optionaldesc: 可选：只设置 rule 模式、日志、IPv6、并发连接与 profile 记忆选项；不包含端口监听category: settingsicon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Koolson/Qure@master/IconSet/Color/Direct.pngmode: rulelog-level: infoipv6: trueunified-delay: truetcp-concurrent: trueprofile:  store-selected: true  store-fake-ip: true